Name: craftAndInsertionFeatures(Quest, Seller, Order)
Description: Craft and Insertion features: Obtain typed models via @Craft and populate mapped model fields to UI controls in one operation using insertion service

Name: preconditionFeatureUsingMuliJourneysWithData(Quest)
Description: Precondition feature: Uses multiple ordered @Journey preconditions with data injection

Name: authenticationFeatureWithCacheCredentials(Quest, Order)
Description: Authentication feature: Automatic login via @AuthenticateViaUi with cache credentials for session re-usage

Name: createOrderPreQuestDatabase(Quest, Order)
Description: Demonstrates database validation in Journey preconditions before test execution

Name: storageFeatureUsingDataFromPreconditions(Quest)
Description: Storage feature: Retrieve storage data captured during test precondition as journeyData pre-arguments

Name: storageFeatureUsingDataFromFluentSteps(Quest, Seller)
Description: Storage feature: Retrieve storage data captured during test UI steps

Name: ripperFeature(Quest)
Description: Ripper feature: Deletes data created in the test

Name: interceptorFeatureUsedForAuthenticateViaUiValidation(Quest)
Description: Interceptor feature: Use built-in response status validation

Name: interceptorFeatureUsedForLateDataCreation(Quest, Seller, Order, Late)
Description: Interceptor feature: Extract intercepted responses data and use it for Late data creation when needed
